OL,3,CDriver, 35, pleads guilty to causing
OL,4,Cdeath of taxi passenger in crash
OL,6,FA driver has admitted causing the
OL,7,Fdeath of a taxi passenger in a crash.
OL,9,FThomas Goulty, 35, the driver of the
OL,10,FVauxhall, and Sarwar Mohammad, 68, who
OL,11,Fthe court heard was driving a Peugeot
OL,12,FExpert Tepee, were both charged over
OL,13,Fthe crash and appeared at Leicester
OL,14,FCrown Court on Monday to enter their
OL,15,Fpleas.
OL,17,FGoulty, of Aikman Avenue, Leicester,
OL,18,Fpleaded guilty to one count of causing
OL,19,Fdeath by careless driving and two
OL,20,Fcounts of causing serious injury by
OL,21,Fcareless driving.
