OL,3,CDriver, 35, pleads guilty to causing
OL,4,Cdeath of taxi passenger in crash
OL,6,FMohammad, who stood in the dock beside
OL,7,FGoulty during the hearing, pleaded not
OL,8,Fguilty to causing death by dangerous
OL,9,Fdriving and also denied two counts of
OL,10,Fcausing serious injury by dangerous
OL,11,Fdriving.
OL,13,FDonna Brighton, 60, from Leicester,
OL,14,Fdied after the taxi she was travelling
OL,15,Fin collided with a silver Vauxhall
OL,16,FAstra in Glenfield Road shortly before
OL,17,F8.30pm on Saturday September 16 2023.
OL,19,FTwo other passengers in the taxi were
OL,20,Fseriously injured.
