OL,6,FA provisional trial date for Mohammad,
OL,7,Fof Willow Brook Road, Leicester, was
OL,8,Fset for November 30 next year.
OL,10,FThe court heard that Goulty is likely
OL,11,Fto be sentenced at the end of
OL,12,FMohammad's trial.
OL,14,FJudge Steven Evans bailed them and
OL,15,Ftold them to return to court for a
OL,16,Ffurther hearing on January 30.
